### Submit a quiz attempt (guide only, first attempt is free)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/quiz-attempts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{guideToken}}

{
  "quizId": "{{quizId}}",
  "responses": [
    {
      "questionId": "REPLACE_WITH_MCQ_QUESTION_ID",
      "selectedOptionId": "REPLACE_WITH_CORRECT_OPTION_ID"
    },
    {
      "questionId": "REPLACE_WITH_TF_QUESTION_ID",
      "selectedOptionId": "REPLACE_WITH_TRUE_OPTION_ID"
    },
    {
      "questionId": "REPLACE_WITH_SA_QUESTION_ID",
      "textResponse": "Orangutan and Pygmy Elephant"
    }
  ]
}

###

### List quiz attempts (guide sees own, admin sees all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/quiz-attempts
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get a specific attempt
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/quiz-attempts/{{attemptId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Grade open questions on an attempt (admin only)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/quiz-attempts/{{attemptId}}/grade
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "grades": [
    {
      "questionAttemptId": "REPLACE_WITH_QUESTION_ATTEMPT_ID",
      "scoreAwarded": 8
    }
  ]
}
